    <p>Yesterday, Seldaek <a href="http://seld.be/notes/psr-4-autoloading-support-in-composer">committed PSR-4 support</a> to <a href="http://getcomposer.org">Composer</a>, as his New Year's Day gift to the PHP community.</p>

<p>So, since I always supported PSR-4 in FIG discussions, and after the <a href="https://drupal.org/node/1971198">tl;dr discussion</a> about it regarding autoloading in Drupal 8, I jumped on the occasion and converted the code base for <a href="http://plusvite.net">PlusVite</a> to PSR-4 to get an idea of how PSR-4 "felt" in practice.</p><p><a href="http://blog.riff.org/2014_01_04_psr4_really" target="_blank">read more</a></p>
